1122
01:00:49,074 --> 01:00:52,164
Especialmente considerando
a namorada adolescente secreta.

1123
01:00:52,202 --> 01:00:53,662
Para de ver a Ellen Abbott!

1124
01:00:53,703 --> 01:00:55,033
Tens de falar comigo!

1125
01:00:57,707 --> 01:01:01,757
